latestIgtvVideos.title: There is no weight limit on love ❤️
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Most girls dream of finding their perfect partner and having a beautiful wedding I thought all these things would happen to me if I lost weight, little did I know how wrong I was! Let me say it loud and clear - you don’t need to change yourself to meet someone, you don’t need to change yourself to have a beautiful wedding. I am so excited to partnering with @weddingwireindia India, a part of @theknotworldwide , to convey  that all women irrespective of their size deserve love and wedding wire India is a place that  believes  #LoveIsLove & it is their mission to  represent all couples irrespective of skin color, body size, sexual orientation, beyond the misrepresentations of beauty & love in our society.

latestPosts.caption:
Years of ordering salad at restaurants because I wanted everyone to think I’m on a diet. Years of eating less in public and coming home and filling my stomach. Years of saying no when offered food but regretting in private. For what? Just because people around you expect you to eat less because of the way you look? Not a single person was concerned when I did fad diets that ruined my health but oh HEYYY this big girl is eating an ice cream so that must be corrected ? Let’s not put labels on food or health or how one looks cause that ain’t your business and never will be.
.
.

This one’s for you daadi ❤️ 
We just won The Cosmopolitan Popular Choice Body-Love Influencer of The Year Award 🏆😁 @cosmoindia 

This means the world to me, not just on a personal level, but for the incredible community that has supported and inspired me ❤️

This is my second time I have won the cosmo award I won it the first time during lockdown and I always wanted to go up on stage and receive it. It was a bittersweet moment cause the first person I wanted to call and say was my daadi. But I know she’s up there showering me with her blessings. Last year was definitely hard for me and you’ll supported me through thick and thin 

This award is a symbol of the power we hold in changing narratives . Each one of you has played a role in this you have shared your stories with me your struggles and triumphs
Let it be a reminder that every voice matters ❤️

latestPosts.caption:
For every girl out there who thought she had to change, you don’t ✨
For years I have fought for change and space in the industry and it’s extremely rare to find these opportunities oh but when I do, I take it in with all my heart ❤️ 
It’s amazing to see the expressions of people when I walk down the runway- some stunned, some filled with smiles and some like what? But no matter what I’m here to stay! I’m here to showcase that everyone deserves a space, a change an opportunity to represent themselves. 
Thank you @archanakochharofficial for this! Your designs are nothing short of beauty but your humility, your attention to detail and your aura won my heart! Will forever be your muse ⭐️ 
@timesfashionweek 
.
.
